#
# If you have an Android phone or tablet, you will be attracted to the convenience and powerfullness of Android desktop widget.
# But will you worry about hard to find the widgets you need, or hard to like the appearance of the widgets.
#
# The AAWW project is initiated in order to solve these problems.
# AAWW (Android App the widget Wizard) is designed to provide Android users with a simple DIY desktop widgets Web platform.
# On the AAWW platform, you can easily create your favorite application shortcuts, browser bookmarks, fast dial, or a combination of them.
#

#
# Here is the instruction of AAWW:
# 
# Step 1: broswer the webside of URL: http://162.105.81.63
#
# Step 2: Choose the name, size of the widget and Your Name, and press "START!"
#
# Step 3: Choose the Layout in the workspace, and create a new component from the component libaray
#
# Step 4: Adjust the position and size of the component with your mouse, and edit other attributes of the component with your keyboard
#
# Step 5: Upload some resource file for customize your own appearance of the widget
#
# Step 6: Edit the function of each component and check the logic of each component
#
# Step 7: Confirm everything, and you can sumbit your widget configuration to the server
#
# Step 8: Then you will get the apk file to install the widget at your android platform
#

#
# Enjoy Yourself About AAWW!
#
